{
  "id": null,
  "title": "üîç EasyFlow - Unified Observability",
  "description": "Single pane of glass for all observability: Prometheus metrics, OpenTelemetry traces, Alertmanager alerts, and system health",
  "tags": [
    "observability",
    "unified",
    "overview",
    "easyflow"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": [
      "10s",
      "30s",
      "1m",
      "5m",
      "15m",
      "30m",
      "1h"
    ],
    "time_options": [
      "5m",
      "15m",
      "1h",
      "6h",
      "12h",
      "24h",
      "2d",
      "7d",
      "30d"
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "üöÄ Service Health Status",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"easyflow-backend\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Backend",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"easyflow-automation\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Automation Worker",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"otel-collector\"}",
          "legendFormat": "OTel Collector",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"prometheus\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Prometheus",
          "refId": "D"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "‚ùå DOWN",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "‚úÖ UP",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "background"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "üìä Workflow Execution Metrics",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(easyflow_span_calls_total[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "Workflow Executions/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(easyflow_span_duration_bucket[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "P95 Latency",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, rate(easyflow_span_duration_bucket[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "P50 Latency",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto"
          },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "‚ö° OpenTelemetry Span Metrics",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(easyflow_span_calls_total[5m])) by (service_name)",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "ops"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "üîî Active Alerts (Alertmanager)",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\"}",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "displayMode": "list"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [
          {
            "desc": true,
            "displayName": "Time"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "üìà HTTP Request Rate",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total[5m])) by (method, status_code)",
          "legendFormat": "{{method}} {{status_code}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "üîó Quick Links",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "## üîó Observability Tools\n\n- **Prometheus UI**: [http://localhost:9090](http://localhost:9090) - Query metrics directly\n- **Alertmanager**: [http://localhost:9093](http://localhost:9093) - Manage alerts\n- **OTel Collector Health**: [http://localhost:13133](http://localhost:13133) - Collector status\n- **Prometheus Metrics Endpoint**: [http://localhost:8889/metrics](http://localhost:8889/metrics) - OTel metrics\n\n## üìä Other Dashboards\n\n- **SLO Dashboard**: View SLO metrics and business reliability\n- **System Monitoring**: Infrastructure metrics\n- **Application Overview**: Application health and performance",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "üíæ Prometheus Storage",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 24
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "prometheus_tsdb_storage_blocks_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "Storage Used",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "bytes",
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1073741824
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5368709120
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "üì° OTel Collector Metrics Received",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 24
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(otelcol_receiver_accepted_spans[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Spans/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "ops"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "üéØ Error Rate",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 28
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(http_requests_total[5m])) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Error Rate %",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "percent",
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "‚è±Ô∏è Request Duration (P95, P99)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 28
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "P95",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "P99",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": false,
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": false,
      "tags": [],
      "targetBlank": true,
      "title": "Prometheus",
